Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中  川添珠姬選手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬選手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的家人到場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請到停車場會面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有聯絡過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之去看看吧  還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束前你就待在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧  比賽要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去給小西前輩加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那川添同學拜拜囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束我們就放你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因為我們讓小西前輩惹上了些奇怪的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠言這種東西真可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  大將
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你拯救部長  也就是紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是室江高的大將川添同學吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是東城高的小西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們下一場的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那三個人是我的後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是仰慕我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有時候卻不分輕重跟要和我對戰的對手開這種玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很高興她們那麼喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭我會好好教訓她們的  這件事請…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更要緊的是不趕快的話比賽就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分鐘前了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  段  你們去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西同學去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西前輩怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  我們去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  要來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球都扔在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽要開始了哦  川添同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君  榮花君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  事情處理完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  本來就沒什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在整隊了  趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒  出列
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！小莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一擊必殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃太多…肚子…好疼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我忘記帶便當過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家給了我好多好多好多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒考慮接下來的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了就吃  給了就吃就吃就吃就吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的氣魄！沒辦法貿然出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！好難受！動不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都一動不動  她們在互相試探！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打呀！聰聰！先下手為強！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星也在注視著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳開始疼起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還要比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不還是出場了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是誰經過那裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是不是帶了手機？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是檢查過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不能把事情交給笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是關在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後鬧大了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且本來不戰而勝就沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到她竟然摔得那麼完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,均衡被破壞了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻上去！聰聰！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東你怎麼了？動作很差勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子真很不妙呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我總是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠足前一定會感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會之前一定會扭傷腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體怎麼這麼不爭氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步伐很亂  移動也畏畏縮縮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼利害的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太輕了啦  裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰莉！給我上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經繼續不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於舒暢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春天！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰莉的春天來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鼴鼠  你好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰莉很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦  聰聰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳步變輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是假裝的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼  有什麼來臨了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洶湧波濤向我湧來啊  各位！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰聰！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了聰聰！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  炸肉餅…很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學  炸蝦條…很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰莉我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步也動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是沒什麼大不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來解決你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地移動的話  就能突然發起進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對手的周圍如同蜜蜂一般飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同蜜蜂一般刺下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！我的必殺技！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦  終於來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暫的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧  朧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔子  小鼴鼠  你們在哪裡？在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  禮美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧  東
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去醫務室？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要在這裡為大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這個沒有取勝的我至少做一些事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平手嘛  你不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一場輪到小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放一百個心的看好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學…你要加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東！不要緊吧！怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力已經相當嫺熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上午的時候不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好輕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不要只想著取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做我能做到的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺地  趕快給我收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子雖然是初學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺振倒是很銳利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊！小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不見了  幻覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點把這個忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我查過室江高的部團計劃表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也真是的  要比賽都不告訴人家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復一下精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中  集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你你都在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是可是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都你很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這不怎麼好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子一平一負
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點嚴峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要贏啊  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在這裡打贏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來減輕你的負擔！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯哦  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上呀！小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你那腳  還能比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不比的話可就無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別棄權了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要被我堂堂正正的打敗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是劍道家的精神對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道這東西如果心境紛亂的話是無法變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  如果要成為優秀的劍道家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神方面同樣也要變得優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱有邪念之心的人是不會變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是劍道家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要打倒她！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  差點到時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束  室江勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  我做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起哦  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就是一勝一敗一平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是關鍵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:16:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井口  不要後退！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙今天好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃！今天幹勁十足呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與平日的集中力完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在母親的事情上的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在全部用在了比賽上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是不怎麼會注意他人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常注意力散漫的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她現在的緊張程度正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱Trance•Kirino
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的氣勢  是無法打倒紀梨乃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次徑直取下兩場！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天紀梨乃果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是紀梨乃真正的實力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃你做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天有神仙保佑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二勝一敗一平  有希望！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一勝二敗一平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說嚴峻  但小西如果能不被擊中一次二連勝的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後按照取得點數的多少是我們贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有取勝的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦！大將！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西同學  拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我敗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就推過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  憑你那腳還能架得住？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你那痛苦的表情呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛不還冷汗直冒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這眼神是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能退！這只是在強忍罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼得更緊一些…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她  認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是…發火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被壓下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這樣的傢伙…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡進攻都會被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不能攻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來守！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用反挑讓她的進攻失效一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定會漏出破綻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子…火焰劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢噢  好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺有效
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺擊啊！是刺擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一次在女子比賽裡面看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是那麼小的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼在這裡突然就…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說她對這場比賽如此認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…總覺得她的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是珠姬的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字還沒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別名嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇本裡也一直都寫著珠姬爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:24:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我真的就叫作「珠姬爸爸」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說在生下珠姬之前就決定了「珠姬」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我從出生起就決定了要叫作「珠姬爸爸」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等深厚的父女羈絆啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我家那珠姬大活躍的下一話是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大賽以及之後的室江高」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提我父母的名字叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「珠姬祖父」和「珠姬祖母」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是騙你的
